'''克里斯蒂安·马特·普利西奇'''（{{lang-en|Christian Mate Pulisic}}；{{bd|1998年|9月18日}}）是一名[[克罗地亚|克羅地亞]]裔[[美國|美國]]職業足球員，目前效力於[[英超|英超]]俱樂部[[車路士|車路士]]並代表[[美國國家足球隊|美國國家足球隊]]參加國際比賽。

2016年4月17日，普利西奇成為德甲史上最年輕進球的外籍球員<ref name=youngest>{{cite web|url=http://www.espnfc.com/borussia-dortmund/story/2852892/christian-pulisic-youngest-non-german-to-score-in-bundesliga|title=Christian Pulisic becomes youngest non-German to score in Bundesliga|work=ESPNFC|accessdate=2016-06-10|archive-date=2019-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190731163847/http://www.espnfc.com/borussia-dortmund/story/2852892/christian-pulisic-youngest-non-german-to-score-in-bundesliga|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同月分也成為德甲史上連續兩輪入球的最年輕的球員<ref>{{cite news|title=Christian Pulisic scores again to become youngest player ever with two Bundesliga goals|url=http://www.foxsports.com/soccer/story/christian-pulisic-scores-again-to-become-youngest-player-ever-with-two-bundesliga-goals-042316|accessdate=23 April 2016|publisher=[[Fox_Sports|Fox Sports]]|date=23 April 2016|archive-date=2020-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404164835/https://www.foxsports.com/soccer/story/christian-pulisic-scores-again-to-become-youngest-player-ever-with-two-bundesliga-goals-042316|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 早年與家族 ==
普利西奇於[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]的[[赫爾希鎮|赫爾希鎮]]出生並長大，父親是在90年代效力[[哈里斯堡|哈里斯堡]]{{link-en|哈里斯堡熱火|Harrisburg Heat|熱火}}的[[室內足球|室內足球]]運動員{{link-en|馬克·普利西奇|Mark Pulisic}}<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.socceramerica.com/article/68133/another-pulisic-headed-to-borussia-dortmund.html| title=Another Pulisic headed to Borussia Dortmund| publisher=SoccerAmerica| date=2016-03-22| accessdate=2016-04-19| archive-date=2017-08-27| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827045438/https://www.socceramerica.com/article/68133/another-pulisic-headed-to-borussia-dortmund.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。普利西奇在7歲時於英國[[北安普敦郡|北安普敦郡]][[布萊克利|布萊克利]]生活了1年，並加入當地球會[[布拉克利鎮足球會|布拉克利鎮]]的青訓系統<ref name="Brackley">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2016/may/31/christian-pulisic-usa-soccer-copa-america-2016|title=Christian Pulisic: the making of a young man ready to step up|publisher=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2016-05-31|accessdate=2016-06-02|archive-date=2019-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803195406/https://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2016/may/31/christian-pulisic-usa-soccer-copa-america-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

他的祖父出生於克羅地亞<ref name=history/>，因此他搬到德國時申請克羅地亞國籍，避免需要申請德國（或[[歐盟|歐盟]]）工作簽證<ref>Siehe Artikel 19 des „Reglement bezüglich Status und Transfer von Spieler“,[http://de.fifa.com/mm/document/affederation/administration/02/55/56/41/regulationsonthestatusandtransferofplayersapril2015g_german.pdf PDF] {{Wayback|url=http://de.fifa.com/mm/document/affederation/administration/02/55/56/41/regulationsonthestatusandtransferofplayersapril2015g_german.pdf |date=20161012231835 }} (430 KB){{de icon}}</ref>。[[克羅地亞國家足球隊|克罗地亚国家队]]曾招揽他，但被婉拒<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.slobodnadalmacija.hr/sport/domaci-nogomet/clanak/id/307420/pulisic-nikada-nece-postati-pulisic|title=Pulisic nikada neće postati Pulišić|accessdate=2019-01-08|date=2016-03-31|work=Slobodna Dalmacija|language=hr|archive-date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412203834/https://slobodnadalmacija.hr/sport/domaci-nogomet/clanak/id/307420/pulisic-nikada-nece-postati-pulisic|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而普利西奇的堂弟威尔·普利西奇（Will Pulisic）同樣是一位足球員，曾入選美國U-17國家隊，司職守門員<ref>{{cite news|title=U.S. under-17 keeper Will Pulisic set to join cousin Christian at Dortmund|url=http://www.espnfc.co.uk/borussia-dortmund/story/2835198/us-u17-keeper-will-pulisic-set-to-join-cousin-at-dortmund|accessdate=18 April 2016|publisher=ESPN FC|date=22 March 2016|archive-date=2019-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190917163408/http://www.espnfc.co.uk/borussia-dortmund/story/2835198/us-u17-keeper-will-pulisic-set-to-join-cousin-at-dortmund|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 俱樂部生涯 ==
=== 多特蒙德 ===
==== 2015–16 ====
[[File:Pulisic170727-2.jpg|thumb]][[巴德拉加茲|巴德拉加茲]]的多特蒙德訓練營內練習]]

2015年1月4日，多德蒙德與年僅16歲的普利西奇簽約，並先讓他在U17隊比賽，之後在同年夏天把他提升至U19隊<ref name="Goal"/>。在15場比賽攻入10球8助攻（U17隊攻入6球5助攻，U19隊攻入4球3助攻）後<ref name="Goal">{{cite web|url=http://www.mlssoccer.com/post/2016/01/31/who-us-international-christian-pulisic-and-how-did-he-make-borussia-dortmund-first|title=Who is US international Christian Pulisic, and how did he make the Borussia Dortmund first team at 17 years old?|work=MLSsoccer.com|accessdate=2016-06-10|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127071705/https://www.mlssoccer.com/post/2016/01/31/who-us-international-christian-pulisic-and-how-did-he-make-borussia-dortmund-first|dead-url=no}}</ref>，普利西奇獲一隊邀請於寒假與他們一起訓練<ref>{{Cite web|title = Der nächste Schritt für Passlack und Pulisic|url = http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/startseite/642270/artikel_der-naechste-schritt-fuer-passlack-und-pulisic.html|website = kicker online|access-date = January 26, 2016|archive-date = 2018-10-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181029155545/http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/startseite/642270/artikel_der-naechste-schritt-fuer-passlack-und-pulisic.html|dead-url = no}}{{de icon}}</ref>。

2016年1月冬歇期期間，普利西奇升入一線隊，並於下半場後備上陣2次，攻入1球1助攻<ref>{{Cite web|title = Christian Pulisic scores in Dortmund win|url = http://sbisoccer.com/2016/01/christian-pulisic-scores-in-dortmund-win|website = Soccer By Ives|access-date = January 26, 2016|language = en-US|archive-date = 2020-10-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201021035711/https://sbisoccer.com/2016/01/christian-pulisic-scores-in-dortmund-win|dead-url = no}}</ref>。1月24日，即普利西奇於一線隊首次亮相後的第二天<ref>{{Cite web|title = Pulisic on the bench for Dortmund's friendly against Sparta Prague. Kick off is at 1:15pm EST, watch it live here. • /r/ussoccer|url = https://www.reddit.com/r/ussoccer/comments/41pvy6/pulisic_on_the_bench_for_dortmunds_friendly/?ref=readnext_8|website = reddit|access-date = January 26, 2016|archive-date = 2018-10-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181029155540/https://www.reddit.com/r/ussoccer/comments/41pvy6/pulisic_on_the_bench_for_dortmunds_friendly/?ref=readnext_8|dead-url = no}}</ref>，他在對上[[柏林聯盟足球俱樂部|柏林聯盟]]的友賽中第1次踢滿全場，並交出1球1助攻的成績表<ref>{{Cite web|title = Christian Pulisic scores second friendly goal of month for Dortmund|url = http://sbisoccer.com/2016/01/christian-pulisic-scores-second-goal-of-month-for-dortmund|website = Soccer By Ives|access-date = January 26, 2016|language = en-US|archive-date = 2020-10-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201026063624/https://sbisoccer.com/2016/01/christian-pulisic-scores-second-goal-of-month-for-dortmund|dead-url = no}}</ref>。6天後，普利西奇在對上[[因戈尔施塔特04足球俱乐部|因戈尔施塔特]]的比賽中首次在聯賽亮相，下半場替補[[阿德里安·拉莫斯|阿德里安·拉莫斯]]上陣，該場比賽他們以2-0獲勝<ref>{{cite news|title=American 17-year-old Christian Pulisic makes Bundesliga debut for Dortmund|url=http://www.espnfc.us/borussia-dortmund/story/2797405/american-christian-pulisic-makes-bundesliga-debut-at-age-17|accessdate=January 30, 2016|publisher=ESPN FC|date=January 30, 2016|archive-date=2020-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609002251/http://www.espnfc.us/borussia-dortmund/story/2797405/american-christian-pulisic-makes-bundesliga-debut-at-age-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外在2月18日，普利西奇則在以2-0戰勝[[波圖足球俱樂部|波圖]]的比賽中首次亮相歐戰賽場<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2016/matches/round=2000659/match=2017168/index.html|title=Dortmund deal Porto heavy blow|work=UEFA.com|accessdate=2016-06-10|archive-date=2019-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031131828/https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2016/matches/round=2000659/match=2017168/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

普利西奇在2016年4月10日的[[魯爾區德比|魯爾區德比]]上陣後，其教練[[托馬斯·圖赫爾|托馬斯·圖赫爾]]評論他說：「普利西奇是第一年挑戰頂級聯賽，他只是個青少年，他首兩場先發上陣的德甲比賽是對[[勒沃庫森|勒沃庫森]]和今天的[[沙爾克04|沙爾克04]]－兩隊皆非容易應付。這表示我們球隊欣賞普利西奇作為職業球員的表現，他在對上[[雲達不萊梅|雲達不萊梅]]和[[利物浦足球俱樂部|利物浦]]的比賽中替補上陣都有著不錯的發揮。他最近狀態看來很好，今天的比賽亦如是。他未能在這種節奏和強度的比賽踢滿90分鐘，是一件十分正常的事<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://screamer.deadspin.com/christian-pulisic-is-more-than-just-the-next-hyped-savi-1770345385|title=Christian Pulisic, The Latest "Savior Of American Soccer," Is More Than Just Hype|last=Redford|first=Patrick|website=Screamer|language=en-US|access-date=2016-04-12|archive-date=2016-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919194239/http://screamer.deadspin.com/christian-pulisic-is-more-than-just-the-next-hyped-savi-1770345385|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。7天後（4月17日），普利西奇射入他德甲的第1球，協助「大黃蜂」以3-0主場擊敗[[漢堡體育俱樂部|漢堡]]，而這一球也使他以17歲212天成為德甲史上最年輕的非德籍進球球員與第4年輕的進球球員<ref name=youngest/>。之後他在下一輪對上[[斯图加特足球俱乐部|斯图加特]]的比賽中再射入1球，使他打破另一個德甲紀錄，以17歲218天成為連續兩輪入球的最年輕球員，另外普利西奇也在這場比賽獲得他職業生涯第1張黃牌<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxsports.com/soccer/story/christian-pulisic-scores-again-to-become-youngest-player-ever-with-two-bundesliga-goals-042316|title=Christian Pulisic scores again to become youngest player ever with 2 Bundesliga goals|work=FoxSports.com|accessdate=2016-06-10|archive-date=2020-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404164835/https://www.foxsports.com/soccer/story/christian-pulisic-scores-again-to-become-youngest-player-ever-with-two-bundesliga-goals-042316|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 2016–17 ===
[[2016年國際冠軍盃|2016年國際冠軍盃]]多特蒙德對上[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]的比賽，普利西奇在下半場補時6分鐘「絕殺」對方，幫助球隊進入互射十二碼階段，但最後以5-6落敗<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espnfc.us/match?gameId=446686|title=Dourtmund vs. Manchester City Recap|work=ESPNFC.com|accessdate=2016-09-09|archive-date=2017-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171008030140/http://www.espnfc.us/match?gameId=446686|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月14日，他在對上[[華沙萊吉亞足球俱樂部|華沙萊吉亞]]的[[2016–17年歐洲冠軍聯賽|歐冠]]比賽中上陣，成為多特蒙德史上最年輕的歐冠首秀球員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxsports.com/soccer/story/christian-pulisic-looked-great-in-his-first-ever-champions-league-match-091416|title=Christian Pulisic looked great in his first ever Champions League match|work=FoxSports.com|accessdate=2016-10-08|archive-date=2020-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204211247/https://www.foxsports.com/soccer/story/christian-pulisic-looked-great-in-his-first-ever-champions-league-match-091416|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10日後，普利西奇在對上[[達斯泰特98體育會|達斯泰特]]的比賽中打進了他16–17賽季的首個進球，同時也助攻2次<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxsports.com/soccer/story/watch-christian-pulisic-score-for-borussia-dortmund-as-the-americans-hot-streak-continues-091716|title=Watch Christian Pulisic score for Borussia Dortmund as the American's hot streak continues|work=FoxSports.com|accessdate=2016-10-08|archive-date=2019-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809135248/https://www.foxsports.com/soccer/story/watch-christian-pulisic-score-for-borussia-dortmund-as-the-americans-hot-streak-continues-091716|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同月28日，他追平[[弗雷迪·阿杜|弗雷迪·阿杜]]和[[蘭頓·當奴雲|蘭頓·當奴雲]]的美國人歐冠上陣記錄，同時也助攻[[安德列·舒賀爾尼|安德列·舒賀爾尼]]攻入「絕殺」一球，該場比賽多特蒙德以2–2戰平[[皇馬|皇馬]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.espnfc.us/borussia-dortmund/story/2960753/borussia-dortmund-christian-pulisic-describes-assist-on-andre-schurrle-goal-an-amazing-moment|title=Christian Pulisic describes Andre Schurrle leveller as 'amazing moment'|access-date=2016-09-29|archive-date=2018-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724032441/http://www.espnfc.us/borussia-dortmund/story/2960753/borussia-dortmund-christian-pulisic-describes-assist-on-andre-schurrle-goal-an-amazing-moment|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月22日，普利西奇在對上[[因戈尔施塔特04足球俱乐部|因戈尔施塔特]]的比賽中替補上場並做出1傳1射，助「大黃蜂」從3–1的瀕臨落敗變為3–3的和局<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espnfc.com/borussia-dortmund/story/2978874/christian-pulisic-dortmund-showed-good-heart-to-fight-back-for-draw |title=Christian Pulisic: Dortmund showed 'good heart' to fight back for draw |work=ESPN FC |date=October 22, 2016 |accessdate=2017-07-16 |archive-date=2019-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190802161644/http://www.espnfc.com/borussia-dortmund/story/2978874/christian-pulisic-dortmund-showed-good-heart-to-fight-back-for-draw |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之後多特蒙德與其續約，直至2020年<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bvb.de/eng/News/Overview/Borussia-Dortmund-also-tie-Christian-Pulisic-to-the-club-for-the-long-term|title=Borussia Dortmund also tie Christian Pulisic to the club for the long-term|date=January 23, 2017|accessdate=January 23, 2017|publisher=Borussia Dortmund|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111231655/https://www.bvb.de/eng/News/Overview/Borussia-Dortmund-also-tie-Christian-Pulisic-to-the-club-for-the-long-term|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.espnfc.com/soccer-transfers/story/3044743/christian-pulisic-extends-borussia-dortmund-deal-until-2020|title=Christian Pulisic extends Borussia Dortmund deal until 2020|date=January 23, 2017|accessdate=January 23, 2017|publisher=ESPN FC|archive-date=2019-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803215927/http://www.espnfc.com/soccer-transfers/story/3044743/christian-pulisic-extends-borussia-dortmund-deal-until-2020|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年3月8日，普利西奇在對上[[本菲卡|本菲卡]]的16強比賽中打進其首個歐聯進球，助球隊取得4–0的勝利，這球也讓他以18歲5月18天的年齡成為隊史最年輕的歐聯進球者<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.espnfc.com/borussia-dortmund/story/3078280/christian-pulisic-becomes-borussia-dortmunds-youngest-champions-league-goalscorer|title=Christian Pulisic becomes Dortmund's youngest UCL goalscorer|date=March 8, 2017|work=ESPN|accessdate=2017-07-16|archive-date=2019-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190801171040/http://www.espnfc.com/borussia-dortmund/story/3078280/christian-pulisic-becomes-borussia-dortmunds-youngest-champions-league-goalscorer|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/soccer-insider/wp/2017/03/08/christian-pulisic-scores-in-uefa-champions-league-details-video/|title=Christian Pulisic scores in UEFA Champions League: details, video|work=Washington Post|date=March 8, 2017|accessdate=2017-07-16|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023173019/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/soccer-insider/wp/2017/03/08/christian-pulisic-scores-in-uefa-champions-league-details-video/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 切爾西 ===
2019年1月2日，普利西奇以6400萬歐元的身價加盟[[車路士|車路士]]，並隨即外借回多特蒙德讓他完成餘下的2018–19賽季賽事<ref>{{cite news |title=Christian Pulisic: Chelsea sign Borussia Dortmund attacker for £58m |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/46734487 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=January 2, 2019 |accessdate=January 2, 2019 |archive-date=2019-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190102100243/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/46734487 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2019年10月26日，英超联赛第10轮，切尔西做客特夫莫尔球场4比2击败伯恩利，拿下各项赛事的7连胜，普利西奇于比赛中上演帽子戏法<ref>{{cite news |last=White |first=Marcus |url=https://www.nbcsports.com/bayarea/soccer/watch-usmnts-christian-pulisic-score-hat-trick-first-chelsea-goals |title=Watch USMNT's Christian Pulisic score hat trick, first Chelsea goals |website=[[NBC_Sports|NBC Sports]] |date=October 26, 2019 |access-date=October 26, 2019 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022160915/https://www.nbcsports.com/bayarea/soccer/watch-usmnts-christian-pulisic-score-hat-trick-first-chelsea-goals |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Mendola |first=Nicholas |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/pulisic-bags-hat-trick-chelsea-182043623.html |title=Pulisic bags hat trick as Chelsea doubles up Burnley |website=[[Yahoo_Sports|Yahoo Sports]] |date=October 26, 2019 |access-date=October 26, 2019 |archive-date=2020-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019151726/https://sports.yahoo.com/pulisic-bags-hat-trick-chelsea-182043623.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本场比赛是普利西奇自8月底以来首次为切尔西首发出场，不仅收获了加盟球队以来首个处子球，并且完成左右脚及头球的完美帽子戏法，是自2010年的[[德罗巴|德罗巴]]之后，首位完成完美戴帽的蓝军球员<ref>{{cite news |last=O'Brien |first=Sean |url=https://talksport.com/football/621277/christian-pulisic-chelsea-perfect-hat-trick-didier-drogba-incredible-stats/ |title=Facts: Christian Pulisic ends Chelsea wait for perfect hat-trick dating back to Didier Drogba era: The incredible stats behind American’s treble |website=[[TalkSPORT|TalkSPORT]] |date=October 27, 2019 |access-date=May 16, 2020 |archive-date=2020-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825174955/https://talksport.com/football/621277/christian-pulisic-chelsea-perfect-hat-trick-didier-drogba-incredible-stats/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。普利西奇以21岁38天的年龄打破了切尔西队史最年轻上演帽子戏法球员的纪录，同时，他成为自2012年邓普西以来，第二位在英超戴帽的美国球员。普利西奇在客场比赛中戴帽，让切尔西自1997-98赛季以来，首次出现一个赛季有两个球员在客场比赛上演帽子戏法。

2020-21球季，普利西奇穿起[[車路士|車路士]]的10號球衣。

2022年2月13日，車路士在[[阿聯酋|阿聯酋]]首都[[阿布扎比|阿布扎比]]舉行的世界冠軍球會盃決賽，加時後以2-1挫[[南美洲|南美洲]]代表[[彭美拉斯|彭美拉斯]]，普利西奇在該場比賽後備登場。

== 國家隊生涯 ==
普利西奇於2013至2015年代表美國U15跟U17國家隊參賽。2013年他在U15國家隊短暫出賽10場，射入2球後升入U17國家隊。在升上美國國家隊前，普利西奇為U17國家隊上陣34次，射入20球，並曾在[[2015年U17世界盃足球賽|2015年U17世界盃]]作為隊長帶領美國隊出賽，同時交出1球3助攻的成績表<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/u17worldcup/matches/round=271783/match=300298362/match-report.html|title=FIFA U-17 World Cup Chile 2015 - Matches - USA 2:2 (2:0) Croatia - FIFA.com|work=FIFA.com|accessdate=2016-06-10|archive-date=2019-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408052315/https://www.fifa.com/u17worldcup/matches/round=271783/match=300298362/match-report.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年3月27日，普利西奇被美國國家隊教練[[尤爾根·克林斯曼|尤爾根·克林斯曼]]召入國家隊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ussoccer.com/stories/2016/03/27/15/57/160327-mnt-klinsmann-adds-zusi-and-pulisic-to-world-cup-qualifying-roster|title=Zusi, Pulisic Added to MNT Roster Ahead of Qualifying Match vs. Guatemala, Presented by Liberty Mutual Insurance, in Columbus|publisher=|accessdate=2016-06-10|archive-date=2019-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424084959/https://www.ussoccer.com/stories/2016/03/27/15/57/160327-mnt-klinsmann-adds-zusi-and-pulisic-to-world-cup-qualifying-roster|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2天後，他在[[2018年世界盃中北美洲及加勒比海區外圍賽第四輪|2018年世界盃資格賽]]對上[[瓜地馬拉國家足球隊|瓜地馬拉]]的比賽中上演了處子秀，於81分鐘替補[[格拉漢姆·祖西|格拉漢姆·祖西]]上場，該場比賽他們以4-0大勝<ref name=history>{{cite news|title=PULISIC MAKES HISTORY AS USA BEAT GUATEMALA|url=http://www.bundesliga.com/en/news/Tournaments/noblmd28-pulisic-youngest-ever-usmnt-player-to-play-world-cup-qualifier-aged-17.jsp|accessdate=April 18, 2016|publisher=Bundesliga|date=March 30, 2016|archive-date=2018-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726205616/https://www.bundesliga.com/en/news/Tournaments/noblmd28-pulisic-youngest-ever-usmnt-player-to-play-world-cup-qualifier-aged-17.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在之後的[[百年美洲盃|百年美洲盃]]，普利西奇亦被克林斯曼加進21人名單中<ref>{{cite news|last1=Floyd|first1=Thomas|title=Pulisic included as USA unveils Copa America squad|url=http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/66/united-states/2016/05/21/23770382/pulisic-included-as-usa-unveils-copa-america-squad|accessdate=May 28, 2016|date=May 21, 2016|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020044713/https://www.goal.com/en-us/news/66/united-states/2016/05/21/23770382/pulisic-included-as-usa-unveils-copa-america-squad|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1星期後，他在美國主場對上[[玻利維亞國家足球隊|玻利維亞]]的友賽中射入1球，使他成為美國國家足球隊史上最年輕的進球球員，該場比賽他們以4-0大勝<ref>{{cite news|title=Dortmund's Pulisic makes history as USMNT rout Bolivia|url=http://www.bundesliga.com/en/copa2016/news/copa2016-dortmunds-pulisic-makes-history-as-usmnt-rout-bolivia.jsph|accessdate=June 10, 2016|publisher=Bundesliga|date=May 27, 2016}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

2016年9月2日，普列錫於[[2018年世界盃外圍賽_(中北美洲及加勒比海區)|2018年世界盃外圍賽]][[2018年世界盃中北美洲及加勒比海區資格賽第四輪|第四輪]]對上[[聖文森特和格林納丁斯國家足球隊|聖文森特和格林納丁斯]]的比賽中梅開二度並助攻1次，助球隊以6-0大勝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mlssoccer.com/post/2016/09/02/us-player-ratings-christian-pulisic-steals-show-qualifying-rout|title=US Player Ratings: Christian Pulisic steals the show in qualifying rout|work=MLSSoccer.com|accessdate=2016-09-09|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026224933/https://www.mlssoccer.com/post/2016/09/02/us-player-ratings-christian-pulisic-steals-show-qualifying-rout|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這讓他成為美國國家隊史上最年輕的世界盃外圍賽進球和梅開二度的球員<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ussoccer.com/stories/2016/09/02/22/51/160902-mnt-players-enter-record-book-as-team-steps-closer-to-hex-in-6-0-wcq-win-at-st-vincent|title=USA Players Enter Record Book as Team Steps Closer to Hex in 6-0 Qualifying Win at St. Vincent|website=www.ussoccer.com|access-date=2016-09-03|archive-date=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723065547/https://www.ussoccer.com/stories/2016/09/02/22/51/160902-mnt-players-enter-record-book-as-team-steps-closer-to-hex-in-6-0-wcq-win-at-st-vincent|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而在之後對上[[千里達及托巴哥國家足球隊|千里達及托巴哥]]的比賽中他則成為美國國家隊史上最年輕的正選球員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espnfc.com/united-states/story/2945175/christian-pulisic-sets-record-as-youngest-american-to-start-world-cup-qualifier|title=Christian Pulisic becomes youngest U.S. player to start World Cup qualifier|work=ESPNFC.com|accessdate=2016-09-09|archive-date=2019-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190802122038/http://www.espnfc.com/united-states/story/2945175/christian-pulisic-sets-record-as-youngest-american-to-start-world-cup-qualifier|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

